	   <tr><td colspan=2>Finaly, some of the stuff from Vulak is being leaked through. Allthough this robe has been on noows.com for quite some time, maybe they will be posting more loot soon (doubt it). And vulak has been killed on two servers actualy ( maybe more, come on silent redemption!) because AL did it on mith. Both AL and FoH have stopped posting loot, and FoH's msgboard has became a whining and sh!t throwing arena. Maybe this will stop it(once again , doubt it)<br><br>Orinvil<br>Warrior of the 17th test of the blade<br>&lt;Evil Unmasked&gt;<br>(Brell Serelis)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
